The topics in this section explain how to manage user accounts and enable the users of a Pivotal Application Service (PAS) runtime on Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF).

##<a id='overview'></a>Overview

Managing an application runtime on PCF means maintaining an environment where app developers have what they need to develop apps. Responsibilites include:

* Inviting and assigning roles to new users.


In addition to these tasks, PCF operators also routinely perform [Day 2 configurations](../customizing/day2.html), to configure or change platform features and integrations&#8212;even well past Day 2.
      
